# 🌾 Crop Yield Prediction Using Weather Data

This project leverages the power of **data science** and **machine learning** to forecast crop yields based on historical weather patterns.  
By analyzing climate conditions, this system aims to help farmers and decision-makers plan better, reduce risks, and maximize agricultural productivity.

---

